76
00:08:36,540 --> 00:08:37,981
Wait. Hold on.

77
00:08:38,061 --> 00:08:39,352
I want to apologize.

78
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:45,960
I didn't do that to you
because Pure told me to.

79
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,600
