80
00:08:50,820 --> 00:08:52,081
He doesn't go out much.

81
00:08:52,531 --> 00:08:53,640
He doesn't take anyone home.

82
00:08:55,860 --> 00:08:58,041
He doesn't even text me back.

83
00:09:00,041 --> 00:09:01,801
So I assumed...

84
00:09:03,220 --> 00:09:06,411
that you're his boy.

85
00:09:10,921 --> 00:09:12,600
I didn't know...

86
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,120
that he was serious...

87
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,291
about you.

88
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,201
That's all I wanted to say.

89
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:27,171
Bye.

90
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,840
Be gentle.

91
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,600
Are you sure you're a doctor?

92
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:11,880
